title: Christian Proposes to Anastasia in New 'Fifty Shades' Video!
text:
Tweet Christian Proposes to Anastasia in New 'Fifty Shades' Video! 
We are just days away from Fifty Shades Darker hitting theaters and a new promo video gives us a first look at the scene in which Jamie Dornan ‘s Christian Grey proposes to Dakota Johnson ‘s Anastasia Steele. 
In the scene, Christian takes Ana into a room filled with flowers and says, “You wanted hearts and flowers?” 
Fireworks blast off and Ana says, “This is amazing.” She turns around and Christian is on his knees with a ring box open and says, “Be mine. Marry me.” 
Watch the romantic scene in the video below!
